title: Jolly LLB 2 Makes 146% Profit At The Box Office
text: Jolly LLB 2 starring Akshay Kumar in lead managed to become a profitable venture at the box office. The courtroom drama was made on a moderate budget of 45 crores including P &A. It currently stands with a collection of 110.71 crores at the domestic box office. Jolly LLB 2 Makes 147% Profit At The Box Office The film has managed to make a profit of 65.71 crores , thus taking its profit percentage to 146% . The Subhash Kapoor directorial was a sequel to his 2013 film Jolly LLB, that starred Arshad Warsi and Boman Irani in lead. TAGS
